&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; (InputStream propStream = Files.newInputStream(Paths.get(filename))) {
                props.load(propStream);
            }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But your stacktrace indicates it&apos;s still using an old version of the clients jar. Is it possible that you didn&apos;t use a clean build?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
